i Morrison's Beloved to Michael Hardt and Toni Negri's Empire. As with everything Michaels writes, The Shape of the Signifier is sure to leave controversy and debate in its wake.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jul 2021) 0aAmerican literaturexHistory and criticismxTheory, etc. 0aAmerican literaturey20th centuryxHistory and criticism. 0aAmerican literaturey21st centuryxHistory and criticism. 0aLiterary form. 0aSignification (Logic) in literature. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / American / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPrinceton University Press eBook-Package Backlist 2000-2013z978311044250240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978140084959840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781400849598423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781400849598.jpg  a978-3-11-044250-2  Princeton University Press eBook-Package Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LT  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK